een speed, features, or native UIs. Ghostty provides all three. In all categories, I am not trying to claim that Ghostty is the best (i.e. the fastest, most feature-rich, or most native). But Ghostty is competitive in all three categories and Ghostty doesn&apos;t make you choose between them. Ghostty also intends to push the boundaries of what is possible with a terminal emulator by exposing modern, opt-in features that enable CLI tool developers to build more feature rich, interactive applications. While aiming for this ambitious goal, our first step is to make Ghostty one of the best fully standards compliant terminal emulator, remaining compatible with all existing shells and software while supporting all of the latest terminal innovations in the ecosystem. You can use Ghostty as a drop-in replacement for your existing terminal emulatorgversionctipldownload_urlxshttps://github.com/pkgforge-dev/ghostty-appimage/releases/download/tip/Ghostty-1.1.4-main%2Bd0e1452-x86_64.AppImagedsizeh59.99 MBhsrc_urlsĀx2https://github.com/psadi/ghostty-appimage/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/psadihprovidesgghosttyglicenseĀcMITkmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Packageģcpkgqgifcurry.appimagehpkg_namehgifcurryfpkg_idx#appimage.github.io.Gifcurry.lettierdiconxŹhttps://raw.githubusercontent.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io/refs/heads/master/database/icons/Gifcurry/icons/scalable/com.lettier.gifcurry.svgkdescriptionxŗGifcurry is your open source video to GIF maker built with Haskell. Import a video, trim, crop, add 