lls are in use, and dozens of other characteristics. It was designed to rapidly scan large networks, but works fine against single hosts. Nmap runs on all major computer operating systems, and official binary packages are available for Linux, Windows, and Mac OS X. In addition to the classic command-line Nmap executable, the Nmap suite includes an advanced GUI and results viewer (Zenmap), a flexible data transfer, redirection, and debugging tool (Ncat), a utility for comparing scan results (Ndiff), and a packet generation and response analysis tool (Nping). This **package** (not nmap !) is maintained at https://github.com/iTrooz/nmap-appimage/gversiond7.95ldownload_urlxXhttps://github.com/iTrooz/nmap-appimage/releases/download/7.95/nmap-7.95-x86_64.AppImagedsizeg9.61 MBhsrc_urlsĀx0https://github.com/iTrooz/nmap-appimage/releaseshweb_urlsĀxhttps://github.com/iTroozhprovidesdnmapglicenseĀxNmap Public Source Licensekmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesáx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Packageģcpkgvnordvpn-linux.appimagehpkg_namemnordvpn-linuxfpkg_idx.appimage.github.io.nordvpn-linux.martijnmicheldiconxŹhttps://raw.githubusercontent.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io/refs/heads/master/database/icons/nordvpn-linux/icons/128x128/nordvpn-electron.pngkdescriptionqNordVPN for Linuxgversionfv0.6.0ldownload_urlxhhttps://github.com/martijnmichel/nordvpn-linux/releases/download/v0.6.0/NordVPN.for.Linux-0.6.0.AppImagedsizei227.05 MBhsrc_urlsĀx7https://github.com/martijnmichel/nordvpn-linux/releaseshweb_urlsĀx https://github.com/martijnmichelhprovidesm